\f3\fs18 \cf4 \super 2\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub So on the first day of the seventh month\'a0Ezra the priest brought the Law\'a0before the assembly, which was made up of men and women and all who were able to 
\f4\i understand
\f1\i0 .\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Quick question \'96 who attended the service? \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Now I know this is going to mess with some of your theology and stuff.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But who were the people who all came together?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}All who were able to UNDERSTAND!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f5\b\fs36 \cf5 RELEVANT\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf6 \'93When we quit the church, I was 13 and I was thrilled.  But not for any ideological reasons.  I was just thrilled because I hated the church.  It scared me.  It was boring.  I had to get up on Sunday.  When I think back, it wasn\'92t relevant to my life.  Superman was relevant to my life.  Baseball was relevant to my life.  \'96 Bill Maher\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It wasn\'92t that the Bible wasn\'92t relevant\'85it\'92s the most relevant engaging book every created.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It was the presentation.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Chicken is chicken is chicken\'85it\'92s not the chicken\'85it\'92s the presentation!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Why we have a Kids Church program.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f5\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We believe in AGE APPROPRIATE TEACHINGS!!!!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Push backs\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Some people think it\'92s because we don\'92t like kids\'85no\'85it\'92s because we love our kids enough to create a whole program around them so they will know who Jesus is and not graduate their faith one day.  \
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They\'92ll LOVE the local church not be bored in it.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I want to be clear\'85it wasn\'92t the pastor\'92s fault.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It was the Bible fault.\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl2
\f5\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It was the programs fault!\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Some people will say I want my whole family to worship together\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Scripture is pretty clear in Romans 12 that our act of worship isn\'92t just what we do for 1 hour here but more importantly what we do during the other 167 hours we have in the week.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If the only time your family \'91worships\'92 together is for one hour on Sunday mornings there are deeper issues then.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Illustration of the mom who wanted her kids to learn hymns but let them listen to 107.1 every day on their drive to school\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Some will bring up Matthew 19:14 \'96 let the little children come to me\'85\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The only way that verse makes any sense is if you\'92re saying I\'92m Jesus\'85and I\'92m not!  Pretty sure we can all agree on that one.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f5\b \cf3 Transition:  Alright I\'92ve beat that into the ground\'85can you tell I\'92m a little passionate about that one?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

