\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub He read it aloud from daybreak till noon as he faced the square before the Water Gate\'a0in the presence of the men, women and others who could 
\f4\i understand
\f1\i0 . \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It uses that word again and when the Bible repeats something it is trying to emphasize the importance of it.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf4 And all the people listened attentively to the Book of the Law.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

