\f4\i clear
\f1\i0\fs15 \super [a]
\fs24 \nosupersub \'a0and giving the 
\f4\i meaning
\f1\i0  so that the people 
\f4\i understood
\f1\i0  what was being read.  Nehemiah 8\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
