\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f5\b\fs36 \cf5 SIMPLE\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Most of the time people find what they are looking for in life\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f5\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Bring your own fork!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}People will say things like I\'92m just not getting fed or I want to go deeper!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They were expecting to get something out of the message.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f5\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}People think Information = Transformation\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf6 John Maxwell says \'93Most people are educated way beyond our level of obedience anyway\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}People think if I just know more then it will change me!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I had a pastor attend a service and walk out and tell people that the sermon was the most simple basic thing he\'92d heard and it wasn\'92t really church.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}My first thought \'96 thank you!  It wasn\'92t to be defensive but to realize he got it and I did what I was trying to do.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Because if I wanted to I could be super deep up here and confuse everyone with Greek and Hebrew words and talk about the tense of stuff.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I could do that and I could come off as smart or impressive\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But that isn\'92t my goal \'96 and we\'92ll get to why in a few minutes\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But my goal is to take the very deep truths that God has given in His word and meditate on them for a months, let the marinate in my mind and figure out how to communicate it in a way that simple and easy to follow!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f5\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}See Applied information = Transformation\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf5 REAL\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Now I don\'92t have a verse from this passage to point to our value and I wasn\'92t going to abuse scripture and try and make it say something it doesn\'92t.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But I don\'92t think I need to.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 17\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub On hearing this, Jesus said to them,\'a0\'93It is not the healthy who need a doctor, but the sick. I have not come to call the righteous, but sinners.\'94  Mark 2:17\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I believe that the church should be the most real place in the world.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}In a world where everyone is posting their perfect selfies the church should be real about their life and where they are at.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This should be the one place you don\'92t have to pretend to have it all together.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Jesus was clear\'85He came for those who are sick.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So we\'92ve tried to create a church where there are no perfect people allowed.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0
\f5\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Where it is ok to not be ok, but not ok to stay there!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0 \cf3 Transition:  So because of all that I LOVE our church.  I\'92m biased I know but I think it is the best church in the area.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 YOU\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0
\f2\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And if you love what we\'92re doing\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you\'92ve been impacted by the messages\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you really believe in what we\'92re doing in creating the most Relevant, Simple, and Real church around\'85then here is your next step in your walk with God?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I\'92m asking you to do everything in your power to bring as many people as you can with you next week.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You won\'92t regret it and there\'92s a good chance it will change someone\'92s life!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We will continue to reach more and more people one way\'85by the people who believe in this church inviting others to come see what we\'92re about.  That is it!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For those who don\'92t believe me I want to do something a little different.  \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition: I want everyone to stand up with me.\
\
\
